---
title: Crispy Cauliflower Dahl with rice and naan
description: This crispy cauliflower dahl is fragrant and flavoursome with just enough heat to give a little kick without knocking you out. You'll be grateful you can mop up every morsel of this dish with the accompanying naan.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF200901_R209_W43_FR_RFR16681761-1_KB_Main_Remove_the_larger_chunks_of_red_pepper_high-dc02346f.jpg
